- [`ca04f3d`](https://github.com/synfig/synfig/commit/ca04f3dfa23ea14d53ea281dd1ff832750ab5fce) fix mainwindow not showing when is offscreen ([#1973](https://github.com/synfig/synfig/issues/1973))
